description: So, I figured since I make a lot of content that is negative about film, I had an idea to try and create a sister series to my Unbridled Rages. The idea is to try and praise the film for the things I thought were great while leaving the flaws out of the analysis, basically the complete inverse of what you often see on the channel. I will pick this back up with other films if you guys enjoy it, I really tried to nail the editing and the script though I wanted to get it out quick to cover the topic. Marvel really did pull something amazing off here, a flawed series but an unprecedented one none the less.Let me know how you feel about the video o/
